HEADWORD: Sucken
<hw>Suck"en</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Socome</er>,
<er>Soc</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Scots Law)</fld> <def>The jurisdiction of a
mill, or that extent of ground astricted to it, the tenants of which are
bound to bring their grain thither to be ground.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

